# title: Tatiana Kochergina / Татьяна Кочергина 1980
# date:  2010-08-07 07:54:46
# tags:  disco, 80s, ukraine, pop

[img/tatiana-kochergina-1980.jpg]
Artist: Татьяна Кочергина
LP title: Уроки музыки
Melodiya / C60-15857-8 / 1980

Groove flavored pop music from Ukraine. Almost all tracks on the LP are interesting ones but it is the single outstanding track there IMO (disco!)

Tracklisting:

A1 Уроки музыки

[tatiana kochergina - ritsarskaya pesnya (fragment).mp3]  (fragment)

[tatiana kochergina - zhenikhi (fragment).mp3]  (fragment)

[tatiana kochergina - nichego ne sluchilos 1980.mp3] 

[tatiana kochergina - volshebnaya skazka 1980.mp3] 

[tatiana kochergina - igray skripka igray 1980.mp3]  a disco gem, recorded with ВИА Кобза's vocal group

[tatiana kochergina - pochemu eto tak 1980.mp3] 

